ิร์ดเพรส  ก็ได้ทำนายว่า  เวิร์ดเพรสจะกลายเป็นรากฐานสำหรับ application ส่วนใหญ่บนอินเตอร์เนท   ลองคิดถึงว่า wordpress จะกลายเป็นเป็น ระบบที่รองรับ app ต่าง ๆ ในโลกอินเตอร์เนท   เหมือนอย่าง android หรือ ios บนมือถือ</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:224:\"http://wordthai.com/%e0%b9%80%e0%b8%a7%e0%b8%b4%e0%b8%a3%e0%b9%8c%e0%b8%94%e0%b9%80%e0%b8%9e%e0%b8%a3%e0%b8%aa%e0%b9%83%e0%b8%99%e0%b9%82%e0%b8%a5%e0%b8%81%e0%b8%ad%e0%b8%b4%e0%b8%99%e0%b9%80%e0%b8%95%e0%b8%ad%e0%b8%a3/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"การแปลไทยสำหรับ wordpress.org\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:170:\"http://wordthai.com/%e0%b8%81%e0%b8%b2%e0%b8%a3%e0%b9%81%e0%b8%9b%e0%b8%a5%e0%b9%84%e0%b8%97%e0%b8%a2%e0%b8%aa%e0%b8%b3%e0%b8%ab%e0%b8%a3%e0%b8%b1%e0%b8%9a-wordpress-org/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:179:\"http://wordthai.com/%e0%b8%81%e0%b8%b2%e0%b8%a3%e0%b9%81%e0%b8%9b%e0%b8%a5%e0%b9%84%e0%b8%97%e0%b8%a2%e0%b8%aa%e0%b8%b3%e0%b8%ab%e0%b8%a3%e0%b8%b1%e0%b8%9a-wordpress-org/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xm